kpi_info.title: REJECTED HS-DSCH RETURN CH FOR INTERACTIVE
kpi_info.use: Number of failed allocations for HS-DSCH transport channel due to lack of radio resources for UL DCH return channel for interactive class connections. After rejection the capacity request is sent back to PS queue and HS-DSCH channel type is not allowed for this capacity request any more. UPDATED:When UL DCH for HS-DSCH return channel cannot be allocated.
